  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who visit the emergency room due to apparent foreign body in esophagus

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients unable to insert a portable endoscopy through the nasal cavity

          -  Patients unable to undergo conventional esophagogastroduodenoscopy for a gold standard
             examination
      </textblock>
